what is the greatest model ever made

00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:17.291
So in 1927 America suffered what Herbert Hoover called

00:00:17.291 --> 00:00:20.792
“the greatest peacetime calamity in the countries history"

00:00:20.792 --> 00:00:22.250
the Great Mississippi Flood

00:00:22.250 --> 00:00:25.250
it flooded seven states, half a million people were displaced

00:00:25.250 --> 00:00:27.000
and it cost the country 

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:30.375
 a third of their entire federal budget at the time

00:00:30.375 --> 00:00:31.792
but mainly it was just terrible

00:00:31.792 --> 00:00:34.375
and so the US Army Corp of Engineers did what they do

00:00:34.375 --> 00:00:36.375
up and down the Mississippi they built levees

00:00:36.375 --> 00:00:38.000
