and making sure all the towns had names

00:02:00.208 --> 00:02:03.750
and so it was this kind of incredible experience

00:02:03.750 --> 00:02:07.208
and families would come to stride across the land

00:02:07.208 --> 00:02:09.458
you could walk from the south to the midwest in five minutes

00:02:09.458 --> 00:02:12.291
six years after they finished it, they were done

00:02:12.291 --> 00:02:16.375
the last test using the Mississippi River model was run

